data.description: This quaint 2-bed, 1-bath home on a generous half-acre presents an idyllic retreat. A detached garage offers additional utility and storage. Recently refreshed with a fresh coat of paint and newly refinished floors, the interior emanates a modern yet cozy vibe. A new water heater ensures efficiency, while the convenience of a new washer and dryer adds contemporary ease to daily chores. Step into the fully fenced backyard, where updated landscaping enhances the outdoor haven, providing both privacy and a serene atmosphere. This property seamlessly blends charm, functionality, and outdoor allure, offering a delightful living experience.
